popt4jlib

Class DblArray1Vector2DblArray1AdapterFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • popt4jlib.DblArray1Vector2DblArray1AdapterFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, FunctionIntf

    public class DblArray1Vector2DblArray1AdapterFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionIntf
    The class is a wrapper class for FunctionIntf objects, that require double[] arguments. This function accepts as argument DblArray1Vector objects instead, and calls the underlying function to be evaluated with the underlying vector's data array.
